## Context
Wave-1 move of the code reorg epic (tracker `0240`). Relocate the Phase-1
corpus-building **entry points** — `catalog_*`, `enrich_*`, `corpus_*`, `scout*`
— into `scripts/harvest/`. Only Tier-3 entry points (per the 0254 audit) move;
imported library modules stay flat.

## Depends on 0253 + 0254
- `0253` installs the relative source-root path model (subdir imports resolve).
- `0254` publishes the Tier-2/Tier-3 list — the contract for what moves.

## Semantic-phase exceptions (architecture.md § "Phase is semantic")
Phase is what a script *does*, not its prefix. Honour the known exceptions when
deciding placement:
- `compute_reranker_calibration.py` — `compute_` prefix but Phase-1 (writes
  reranker calibration to `CATALOGS_DIR`); it is a harvest/Phase-1 script.
- Any `enrich_*`/`corpus_*` that the 0254 audit flagged as imported stays flat.
Do not move a script into `harvest/` on prefix alone — check the audit's phase
classification.

## Relevant files
- `scripts/catalog_*.py`, `scripts/enrich_*.py`, `scripts/corpus_*.py`, `scripts/scout*.py`
- `docs/repo-layout.md` — Tier-2/Tier-3 audit table (0254)
- `.claude/rules/architecture.md` § Phase is semantic — the exception list
- `Makefile` + Phase-1 `.mk`/build scripts — corpus target script paths to repoint

## Actions
1. `git mv` each Tier-3 harvest entry point into `scripts/harvest/`.
2. Repoint every Make / build script path to the new location.
3. Leave Tier-2 library modules and the semantic-phase-flagged scripts flat.

## Test
- `make -n` for one corpus target yields the same prereq graph — only the path
  segment changes.
- Moved entry points import + run under `PYTHONPATH=scripts:libs/openalex-corpus/src`.
- `make check` green.

## Invariants
- Only Tier-3 entry points move; Tier-2 modules + semantic exceptions stay flat.
- No top-level `src/`; no `python -m`; flat module names unchanged.
- Phase separation: a harvest move must not let Phase-1 be triggered by a later
  phase (feedback `phase_separation`).
- One logical move per PR (this ticket = the harvest move only).

## Exit criteria
- All Tier-3 `catalog_*`/`enrich_*`/`corpus_*`/`scout*` entry points under
  `scripts/harvest/`; semantic exceptions correctly left flat.
- Every Make/build script path repointed; no dangling reference.
- `make check` green.

